	"description": "This project is the result of applying the concepts learned in the [Fullstack Next.js v4 course by Brian Holt for Frontend Masters](https://frontendmasters.com/courses/fullstack-app-next-v4/). While the original project consisted of a simple wiki page, this project adapts those concepts to a modding website, similar in concept to moddb.com, where users can create and share mods for a game. It uses `02-complete-ui` from the [course project repo](https://github.com/btholt/fullstack-next-wiki) as a starting point and builds upon it to create a more complex application.",
